<font class='uk-text-large'>CivY is an Intelligent ( curriculum vitae ) C.V. management System. It allows to create and maintain a complete web based C.V. for an individual summarizing his/her academic profile and work history, which can be accessed through the internet. It has advanced features such as Print friendly hard copy and menu based site administration to overcome
the disadvantages of existing Paper Based Resumes.
</font><font class='uk-text-warning uk-text-bold'>This website is a live example of CivY at work ... </font>